\documentclass[a4paper]{article}
\usepackage{lipsum}
\usepackage{hyperref}
\begin{document}
\ref{sec:foo}
\lipsum[1-20]
\section{Foo}
\label{sec:foo}
\lipsum[1]
\end{document}

The above works with both pdflatex and latex->dvips->ps2pdf on my
MiKTeX system. You must be doing something differently.


